Package: LigandReceptor
Title: Predict Ligand-Receptor Pairs from scRNAseq data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alejandro",
           family = "Chibly",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alejandro.chibly@gmail.com")
Description: Package creates a table of ligand-receptor pairs for all cell populations in 
          a single-cell RNAseq experiment. It uses as input a table of cell markers generated with 
          the FindAllMarkers function from SEURAT. A chord plot can be generated using the circlize package.
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    circlize,
    dplyr,
    reshape2
Suggests:
    knitr,
    devtools,
    roxygen2,
    testthat
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
